{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136420, "create_time": 1653240464, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "太长不看", "timestamp": 1653240464}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136422, "create_time": 1653240502, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "确实下功夫调查研究了", "timestamp": 1653240502}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136426, "create_time": 1653240588, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "同样好奇，为什么疫情反复爆发", "timestamp": 1653240588}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136429, "create_time": 1653240648, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "在可预见的情况下，还将持续下去", "timestamp": 1653240648}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136434, "create_time": 1653240736, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "结尾句：“答案很简单，这场没有硝烟的战争中，真正的双方，从来都不是“人类”与“病毒”，而是全世界坚持科学抗疫的人们，与全世界的“病毒爱好者”们。”", "timestamp": 1653240736}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136438, "create_time": 1653240872, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "反驳还是要从核心论点来讲，摘取一些情绪化的语句不太好。比如我觉得现有政策更大程度抑制了消费；但是我觉得文中对于医学角度的分析是有参考价值的", "timestamp": 1653240872}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136441, "create_time": 1653240942, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Carol: 因为岳各庄 因为华亭酒店", "timestamp": 1653240942}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136444, "create_time": 1653241012, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 因为人类自身有局限性，人总会疲劳，总会出错", "timestamp": 1653241012}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136451, "create_time": 1653241232, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "写的很好", "timestamp": 1653241232}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136454, "create_time": 1653241312, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Eve: 好文，现在还是要团结起来想办法", "timestamp": 1653241312}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136466, "create_time": 1653241565, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "看了几个段落，查资料确实下了功夫，但夹带私货确实太明显了，只选取了有利于自己观点的数据列出来。对自己不利的，比如经济，就敷衍地一笔带过，或者全怪上海，问题是上海现在搞成这样根本原因就是想兼顾经济和防疫。再比如说传染病，把霍乱、梅毒和新冠相提并论，是不合适的，病原学和流行病学特征都相差太多了，更合适作为类比的应该是流行性感冒，作者就绝口不提。", "timestamp": 1653241565}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136486, "create_time": 1653242170, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 作者专门拿了一个大段来论证共存政策之后的经济只会比现行清零更差啊", "timestamp": 1653242170}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136487, "create_time": 1653242183, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "霍乱、鼠疫、结核、白喉、梅毒、淋病全都是由细菌引起的，不是病毒。天花病毒是DNA病毒。而新冠是RNA病毒，人类历史上战胜过的RNA病毒，据我所知只有SARS。至于新冠的非典的区别，这位作者又一笔带过了。", "timestamp": 1653242183}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136489, "create_time": 1653242223, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 你再仔细看看，他论证的是“可能更差”，隐含的意思是“可能更差也可能更好”", "timestamp": 1653242223}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136490, "create_time": 1653242253, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 深圳为什么能两三周结束，上海搞成这样是不是还是上海的责任", "timestamp": 1653242253}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136493, "create_time": 1653242283, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: ？那可是找不到更好的例子啊", "timestamp": 1653242283}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136496, "create_time": 1653242363, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 而且作者也提到了对于流行性感冒的超额死亡是大概十倍啊...", "timestamp": 1653242363}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136497, "create_time": 1653242380, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "超额死亡那里就考虑流感了", "timestamp": 1653242380}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136498, "create_time": 1653242388, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 对比数字那段，美国的经济数字是比中国更好的，作者说“美国赢麻了、中国输麻了”。我不知道是阴阳怪气还是试图蒙混过关。“回到正题”那一段表达的就是可能更好也可能更差。", "timestamp": 1653242388}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136503, "create_time": 1653242482, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 那你怎么解释北京一个月了还没有结束的迹象？因为北京也在“瞻前顾后、畏首畏尾、幻想着低成本解决问题”？", "timestamp": 1653242482}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136505, "create_time": 1653242519, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 我觉得你说得对", "timestamp": 1653242519}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136506, "create_time": 1653242537, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob & Eve: 我指的是08批判投降主义那一段", "timestamp": 1653242537}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136507, "create_time": 1653242575, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 其实前几天差不多结束了，朝阳已经快清零了，顺义也快清零了，房山都快清零了，然后突然一个岳各庄聚集疫情(有隐瞒行程等等)，丰台海淀就全爆了", "timestamp": 1653242575}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136510, "create_time": 1653242616, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 明明是“数字更好”，像是什么“名义”gdp增速，“就业率”...", "timestamp": 1653242616}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136513, "create_time": 1653242679, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Eve: \n![](https://bafybeibwzrnjveejf5hchxi5e7wnzynxxfqan366xnlucd5rssymm7az4y.ipfs.dweb.link/?filename=mmexport1653242647716.png&filetype=image%2Fpng) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafybeibwzrnjveejf5hchxi5e7wnzynxxfqan366xnlucd5rssymm7az4y)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1653242679}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136519, "create_time": 1653242754, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 这就有双标之嫌，数字对你的观点有利的时候，你引用数字，数字对你的观点不利的时候，你说数字只是数字而已。等你到了快毕业要找工作的时候，你就会知道中国失业率比美国高一大截是否只是数字了。", "timestamp": 1653242754}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136523, "create_time": 1653242855, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "经济方面拿美国增速和中国增速比。。美国疫情之前也是这个增速，中国可一直在走下坡路", "timestamp": 1653242855}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136535, "create_time": 1653243028, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 你说的没错，支持清零的同学常常会这么认为，只要把少数害群之马全部抓住，把所有漏洞都堵住，就会万事大吉了（比如华亭宾馆，比如你所说的岳各庄有瞒报行程等）。我的回应是，要承认人自身的局限性，人总是会疲劳、会犯错的，漏洞也总是堵不完的。在北京加码到这个程度的情况下，农商银行、中建十一局、岳各庄市场、最新的东方新天地……聚集性疫情还是能不断发生，我觉得足够说明问题了。还有天津，1月来一波，3月来一波，5月又来一波。", "timestamp": 1653243028}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136548, "create_time": 1653243147, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 我是码农专业，我的专业告诉我，计算机一般不会犯错，但人总是会犯错的，程序员会犯错，用户也会犯错。设计一个系统的时候，一定要考虑到人犯错的可能性。如果一个系统要指望所有人都永远不犯错才能正常运行，那这个系统的设计是有问题的，容错性、鲁棒性差。", "timestamp": 1653243147}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136563, "create_time": 1653243306, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 况且现在海淀、东城的社会面新增，到底能不能把责任推给瞒报行程，我暂且蒙在鼓里", "timestamp": 1653243306}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136577, "create_time": 1653243485, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我睡觉了，如果想接着聊，我明天有空再回复", "timestamp": 1653243485}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136638, "create_time": 1653244804, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: \n>？那可是找不到更好的例子啊”\n\n——作者找不到合适的例子来证明自己的论点，这不恰恰说明了作者的论点有问题吗？\n\n>\n\n这个问题上，如果一定要用类比推理的话，我的观点是，RNA病毒变异快，呼吸道传染病容易传播，根据这些特点，新冠应该类比流感，人类没有战胜流感而是长期和流感共存，由此可见人类也无法战胜新冠、应该和新冠共存。而这个作者试图类比霍乱、鼠疫、结核、白喉、梅毒、淋病，证明人类能战胜新冠、不应和新冠共存，这是站不住脚的。", "timestamp": 1653244804}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136689, "create_time": 1653245740, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "朴石被查进一步说明了确实是存在一些病毒爱好者在从中浑水摸鱼", "timestamp": 1653245740}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 136708, "create_time": 1653245979, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "病毒爱好者这个称呼太情绪化了，甚至有点人身攻击的味道。照这样的话，共存派也可以把清零派称为轮流封控爱好者、每日核酸爱好者、失业爱好者、经济崩溃爱好者。这样不好吧。", "timestamp": 1653245979}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 137049, "create_time": 1653270048, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 找不到经济上共存更好的例子...", "timestamp": 1653270048}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 137051, "create_time": 1653270103, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Francis: 美国也保持了好几年百分之三四的增长，疫情之后才掉到1到0左右的", "timestamp": 1653270103}], "create_time": 1653240433, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653270103, "likenum": 12, "n_attentions": 12, "n_comments": 36, "pid": 46916, "poll": null, "reply": 36, "text": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/fF0mlveGMd5AYSog7a7opw", "timestamp": 1653240433}}